{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:13:38.122146+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on my investigation of the repository, here's a walkthrough of the database migrations:\n\n## Migration Overview\n\nThe repository has a **`MIGRATION_HISTORY.md`** file that documents 6 migrations that have been applied in production. However, only **3 migration files are currently present** in the `migrations/` directory—the rest (004-006) have been archived per the documentation.\n\n---\n\n## Migrations in Order\n\n### 1. `001_create_users.sql` — Initial Users Table\n**Applied:** 2024-11-04\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE users (\n    id           BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n    email        TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n    display_name TEXT,\n    created_at   TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n```\nCreates the foundational `users` table with:\n- Auto-incrementing `id` (BIGSERIAL)\n- Unique `email` constraint\n- Optional `display_name`\n- Auto-timestamped `created_at`\n\n---\n\n### 2. `002_create_sessions.sql` — Sessions Table with Foreign Key\n**Applied:** 2024-12-10\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE sessions (\n    id          UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    user_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n    issued_at   TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),\n    expires_at  TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n);\n```\nCreates the `sessions` table with:\n- UUID primary key\n- Foreign key to `users(id)` with `ON DELETE CASCADE`\n- Timestamps for session issuance and expiration\n\n---\n\n### 3. `003_add_session_index.sql` — Session User Index\n**Applied:** 2025-01-22\n```sql\nCREATE INDEX idx_sessions_user_id ON sessions(user_id);\n```\nAdds an index on `sessions.user_id` to speed up lookups by user.\n\n---\n\n### 4-6. Archived Migrations (No Longer in Directory)\n\nAccording to `MIGRATION_HISTORY.md`, these were applied but have since been archived:\n\n| Migration | Applied | Purpose |\n|-----------|---------|---------|\n| `004_partition_users.sql` | 2025-02-18 | Range-partitions the `users` table by `created_at` (monthly) |\n| `005_archive_legacy_sessions.sql` | 2025-03-05 | Moves sessions older than 90 days to a `sessions_archive` table |\n| `006_grant_readonly_role.sql` | 2025-04-12 | Creates an `app_readonly` role with read-only grants |\n\nNote: The `migrations/archived/` directory referenced in the docs doesn't exist in the current repo, so those archived files appear to have been removed entirely.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 839, "prompt_tokens": 5054, "total_tokens": 5893, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 228, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4608, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0009405288, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002105988, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00072993}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780963994-OC7JT0j4GNEUrI9W6f9s", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9b9-eaf9-7790-a26f-bafee80cfd39-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5054, "output_tokens": 839, "total_tokens": 5893, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 4608}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 228}}}}]}}}
